item.title: [317]Compile Error! plz help..[jst 1 error]
item.dc:creator: @zyle1992 Zymus
item.description:
@zyle1992 wrote:

[quote=“david7147, post:9, topic:342882”][quote author=zyle1992 link=topic=439286.msg3228225#msg3228225 date=1275794985]

Instead of deleting the last } try posting the code you added and got the error from

The last compile error clearly says that there’s already ‘abyte0’ declared in the method…

He wouldn’t have gotten that error if he hadn’t deleted the last }

Dude… READ THE FUCKING ERROR! It says that in method57, there are two local variables named ‘abyte0’.
[/quote]
Dude, read the FIRST ERROR that he had BEFORE he deleted the BRACKET[/quote]

And he FIXED that error when he deleted that bracket. Structure errors are thrown before syntax error, which are thrown before naming errors. The first error was a structure error, there were no syntax errors, so now it’s showing us the naming errors.
